{"tid":903796,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼吸毒新趨勢 垃圾堆中翻找用過衛生棉　「水煮M巾」代替毒品帶來輕飄飄幻覺","createTime":"2018-11-16T00:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T01:17:07.000Z","uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b7251056c8bd625dbc7de2b02776070b7d7f4be9","tid":903796,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T00:15:32.000Z","msg":"印尼吸毒問題嚴重，據印尼大學2016年研究顯示，當地吸毒者達640萬人，每日約有33人死於濫用毒品。當地年輕人近年興起一種不可思議的毒品，就是在垃圾堆中找出使用過的衛生巾，放入熱水中煮後再把「M巾水」飲落肚，號稱可以代替毒品，帶來輕飄飄的感覺！<br />\n<br />\n緝毒局官員：毒素氯氣帶來幻覺<br />\n<br />\n據《雅加達郵報》報道，印尼警方日前逮捕一群年輕人，他們以「M巾水」模仿吸毒的感覺。他們會先在垃圾堆中翻找用過的衛山巾，然後用水煮過後，待涼掉後就喝掉。<br />\n<br />\n飲用「M巾水」雖然聽起來很噁心，但印尼國家緝毒局的官員蘇比蘭多（Adj. Sr. Comr. Suprinarto）指衛生巾經煮沸後，水中會含有毒素氯氣（chlorine），飲後會有「飄飄然」及飛起來的幻覺，和吸毒的感覺很相似，而且也比真實的毒品便宜。<br />\n<br />\n印尼警方目前已經在雅加達、西爪哇、中爪哇各地逮捕了多名吸食毒品年輕人，當中多名被捕人士都以類似方法「吸毒」。"},{"pid":"87a533cab93c701667078b968f7aa1a046852adc","tid":903796,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T00:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2205000/2207063/AFP20151213_308740_01_02_1024_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2205000%2F2207063%2FAFP20151213_308740_01_02_1024_600.jpg&h=5d5354e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印尼的年輕人在垃圾堆中找用過的衛生巾，煮滾後當平價毒品。<br />\n<br />\n混合濫用驅蚊劑和咳藥水飲醉<br />\n<br />\n事實上這種吸毒方法並不是新現象，早在2016年，印尼警方已經查獲類似事件，在2017年起案例更有增加的跡象，但現時當地仍未有相關法律管理。除此之外，有青少年也會找酒精的代替品，企圖得到飲醉的感覺。"},{"pid":"244ad6bfd2f2076004ddfe019002cc8fa294b13e","tid":903796,"uid":144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T00:19:14.000Z","msg":"source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbba2934cb244090125879027a41e2d37379a23","tid":903796,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T00:20:28.000Z","msg":"蘋果：【極噁心】印尼青年「水煮衛生巾」當毒品 當局嚴打<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181112/58902074\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181112%2F58902074&d=vasDmUa7TybUVXifsIhVugtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=6efd9865\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181112%2F58902074&h=e8049966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181112/58902074</a>"},{"pid":"465c99252de9bd0a9803e6fd07bbebfca75f3ab6","tid":903796,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T00:21:01.000Z","msg":"Topick:<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2207063/垃圾堆中翻找用過衛生棉%E3%80%80「水煮M巾」代替毒品帶來輕飄飄幻覺\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2207063%2F%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E5%A0%86%E4%B8%AD%E7%BF%BB%E6%89%BE%E7%94%A8%E9%81%8E%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E6%A3%89%25E3%2580%2580%E3%80%8C%E6%B0%B4%E7%85%AEM%E5%B7%BE%E3%80%8D%E4%BB%A3%E6%9B%BF%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86%E8%BC%95%E9%A3%84%E9%A3%84%E5%B9%BB%E8%A6%BA&d=vasDmUa7TybUVXifsIhVugtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=123e2d56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2207063/垃圾堆中翻找用過衛生棉%E3%80%80「水煮M巾」代替毒品帶來輕飄飄幻覺</a>"},{"pid":"ccbb751dca60085cf30cf9af18ba472498981e45","tid":903796,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"244ad6bfd2f2076004ddfe019002cc8fa294b13e","tid":903796,"uid":144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T00:19:14.000Z","msg":"source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T00:22:09.000Z","msg":"抻手黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a63c8d4e1a7b47f78a1a7152a4f49ca6cbb40e","tid":903796,"uid":42064,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ccbb751dca60085cf30cf9af18ba472498981e45","tid":903796,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid"